      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Gregory Strong</b>\n</p><p><b>Gregory Strong</b>,<br />\nan American professional software developer, Chess enthusiast, and author of <a href=\"/ChessV\" title=\"ChessV\">ChessV</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>, an <a href=\"/Category:Open_Source\" title=\"Category:Open Source\">open source engine</a> that plays over 50 <a href=\"/Chess#Variants\" title=\"Chess\">chess variants</a> with various board sizes, as well as Orthodox Chess <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. \nHe is further working on a chess engine dubbed <a href=\"/index.php?title=Quadrox&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Quadrox (page does not exist)\">Quadrox</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2009\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2009</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gregory_Strong&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2009\">2009</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gregory_Strong&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2009\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=25795\">Evaluating every node?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 03, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=25917\">Bitboards / move generation on larger boards</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 09, 2009&#160;»  <a href=\"/Bitboards\" title=\"Bitboards\">Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=26446\">64-bit development in Linux</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 08, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Linux\" title=\"Linux\">Linux</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=26632\">Extensions, anyone?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 20, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Extensions\" title=\"Extensions\">Extensions</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=27122\">Different handling of ALL / CUT nodes</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 22, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Node_Types\" title=\"Node Types\">Node Types</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30471\">Problem with functions not inlining</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 04, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/SSE2\" title=\"SSE2\">SSE2</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=30742\">Kindergarten Bitboard help</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 22, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Kindergarten_Bitboards\" title=\"Kindergarten Bitboards\">Kindergarten Bitboards</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=35356\">Xiangqi evaluation function</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 09, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Chinese Chess</a>, <a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gregory_Strong&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36692\">This is totally weird ... Don't understand at all</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 13, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/Quiescence_Search\" title=\"Quiescence Search\">Quiescence Search</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63489\">ChessV 2.0 - open source GUI and engine for chess variants</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 19, 2017</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63801\">multi-pv analysis</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 23, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Principal_Variation#MultiPV\" title=\"Principal Variation\">Multi-PV</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67775&amp;start=8\">Re: On-line engine blitz tourney June</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 23, 2018</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gregory_Strong&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.chessvariants.com/index/displayperson.php?personid=GregoryStrong\">Greg Strong - Chess Variant Pages Homepage</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gregory_Strong&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.chessvariants.com/index/displayperson.php?personid=GregoryStrong\">Greg Strong - Chess Variant Pages Homepage</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ChessV\">ChessV from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36692\">This is totally weird ... Don't understand at all</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 13, 2010</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=67539&amp;start=7\">Re: On-line engine blitz tourney May</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Gregory Strong</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 27, 2018</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301085323\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.012 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.012 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 79/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 170/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:7040-0!canonical and timestamp 20260